slightly superior paella to El Suquet de l'Almirall.  rice a little less al dente, similar flavor, but little less salty.  cooked a little faster, 2 person minimum thus pricier.  mussels a little oceany.  the bread is perfect, so was the burrata salad with arugula and tomato with pesto, excellent.  calamari fried with tartar also done well.
